title: Episode 325: WHY YOU BEING WIERD TO ME!? (Feat. Don't Call Me White Girl)
itunes:title: Episode 325: WHY YOU BEING WIERD TO ME!? (Feat. Don't Call Me White Girl)
description:
Viral sensation, Don't Call Me White Girl joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote her podcast and comedy tour. You definitely recognize DCMWG from her 'why you being weird to me' video, as well as her p*ssy pap-ready and ugly baby video. The ladies discuss a range of topics including why and how DCMWG got caught cheating on both of her fiance's, her time spent in jail, handling her business now that her career is off to the races, and much more. Enjoy!
